  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>While the waves pound on the stony beach</l>
            <l>our remaining time keeps running one minute after the other one gets lost</l>
            <l>one minute after the other one gets lost</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>That way the toil gets spread.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Cribs were once the center of hope</l>
            <l>trying to become mature to get crowned</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>The darkness fights this marvellous event</l>
            <l>and time which already passed by shows its surprising talent.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Time hardens the youth's process of growing up</l>
            <l>and makes them becoming beautiful,</l>
            <l>time is <choice><orig>dependant</orig><reg>dependent</reg></choice> on natural rarities</l>
            <l>it just waits for us to grow so it can cut us down.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>Still, my sonnet should keep existing and bring hope to make sure you know</l>
            <l>your worth although time never stops running.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
